{"tid":1537369,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"律師會：公然違抗法庭禁制令是對法治的侮辱","createTime":"2019-09-04T01:57:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T03:14:44.000Z","uid":314491,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"04370de3a84e1b73bb83e137b48a7d4884510c0e","tid":1537369,"uid":314491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:57:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/69517166_10218051960442983_5744093861580374016_o_3Svox_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F69517166_10218051960442983_5744093861580374016_o_3Svox_1200x0.png&h=09c77a84&s={SIZE}\" />     在機場獲批臨時禁制令的情況下，反對《逃犯條例》修訂的示威者上周日發起堵塞機場道路行動。香港律師會發聲明指，癱瘓香港國際機場通道、堵塞馬路及破壞公共交通和鐵路車站的行為，是公然違抗正在生效的法庭禁制令，認為公然違抗法庭禁制令是對法治的侮辱。<br />\n<br />\n律師會表示，任何人士忽視遵守或遵照法庭禁制令，或任何人士援助或煽動、協助或教唆他人違反法庭禁制令，可能會被控以藐視法庭。<br />\n<br />\n律師會又譴責各種形式的非法暴力；特別是對警察使用汽油彈、對警察家屬擬作出攻擊及欺凌其在校園的子女，並留意到公眾嚴正關注警方對港鐵站內的乘客施加不必要武力一事。律師會促請相關執法部門認真正視有關事件，並徹底和公正地進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n律師會呼籲香港特區政府採取措施，以解決整個社會的關注。社會各界不同人士已向政府提出了一些建設性的建議。律師會促請政府與市民進行公開對話，盡快尋求恢復香港和平與安寧的解決方案。"},{"pid":"d825455191c3627f95e95cab7778ed4fd57153f5","tid":1537369,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:58:03.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7d7cc4dfac738629f4555ad00437c30ca2576ad","tid":1537369,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:58:55.000Z","msg":"公然濫用呢"},{"pid":"349659afb11b13b126a71bc6d96096f16f45e49c","tid":1537369,"uid":294844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:00:19.000Z","msg":"而家都冇法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c93a0ca84f149d6f6a76264e324665ecf71edd","tid":1537369,"uid":267425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:03:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>解散警隊 刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fLDFcUN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfLDFcUN.jpg&h=350c6ca1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7931a7fb52335fa893c8c5cbcba7b635ee9272a","tid":1537369,"uid":221490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:05:48.000Z","msg":"梁振英5000萬  鄭若驊僭建  劏房波<br />\n警察衣家濫權<br />\n你又唔7出來講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaee196fdb1145bfed3cff656b8abc605fa13a2c","tid":1537369,"uid":26191